Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.69,0:00:12.20,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.25,0:00:17.83,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,照亮了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:21.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs38\pos(450,390)\1c&HFFFFFF&}海底两万里 / {\fs18}蓝宝石之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.09,0:00:30.13,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌懦弱的人 无法背叛蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.18,0:00:37.31,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在做梦之前 我想翱翔天际
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.35,0:00:44.19,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心中的音乐盒开启 发出声响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.24,0:00:51.62,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一点一滴演奏出幸福与勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.66,0:01:00.29,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.34,0:01:05.63,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,言语是永远的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.67,0:01:10.55,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't forget to try in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:16.48,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱比宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.52,0:01:22.10,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更能照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.01,0:01:29.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,时值公元1889年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.15,0:01:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在巴黎万国博览会上认识的强、娜蒂亚与大王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.38,0:01:37.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一同前往强在勒阿弗尔的家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.65,0:01:40.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是企图夺取『蔚蓝之水』 的邪恶三人组
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.69,0:01:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,驾驶着万能战车·葛兰坦 再度找上门来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.43,0:01:48.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强他们搭乘自己制作的飞机 好不容易逃了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.53,0:01:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惜引擎故障 只好迫降在海上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:55.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚的『蔚蓝之水』
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.14,0:01:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,究竟隐藏着什么样的秘密呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.44,0:02:04.07,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,#03 神秘大海兽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.20,0:02:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 再这样下去会沉的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.27,0:02:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以我才会像这样 尽全力在排水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.41,0:02:39.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在明明忙到想跟猫借手来用了 (意指『忙得团团转』)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.82,0:02:46.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 那个是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.67,0:03:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.84,0:03:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.88,0:03:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前方发现遇难者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:11.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.35,0:03:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,引擎停止 右舵15度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.03,0:03:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,准备救助遇难者\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们要停下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.13,0:03:32.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们有救了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.17,0:03:40.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好壮观
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.18,0:03:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没事吧？只有你们两个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.88,0:03:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.68,0:03:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有一只狮子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.19,0:03:53.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.26,0:03:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有办法过来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.49,0:03:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:03:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 你这艘船还真怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样根本跑不快喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.46,0:04:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是啦 这是飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.40,0:04:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,飞机？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.77,0:04:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,飞机是指在天上飞的那个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.83,0:04:40.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要紧 坐着就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.40,0:04:41.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.07,0:04:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,欢迎你们来到亚伯拉罕号
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.41,0:04:46.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是舰长梅比鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这位是副舰长 赫兰少校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.44,0:04:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢您 梅比鲁舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.95,0:04:52.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多亏您 我们才能得救
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.38,0:04:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用不着道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.28,0:04:57.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这只是军人的本分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.39,0:05:00.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对了 那架航空器是你做的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的 是我和姑丈一起做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.19,0:05:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们对航空器也颇有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以让我们做点调查吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗…去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.77,0:05:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.27,0:05:20.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就请你们说说 为什么会漂到这里来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.81,0:05:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.79,0:05:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大致上我已经了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个三人组 想对你们不利是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的 舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:43.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然追着这样的孩子到处跑 真是群过份的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:48.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看来有人在谈论我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.57,0:05:53.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,桑森
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.68,0:05:55.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,『美丽』这个词
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.78,0:05:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是为了我而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.05,0:06:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 是为了我而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.39,0:06:08.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都快要进入20世纪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们有时间说这个的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.76,0:06:18.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还不快去把那架飞机找到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.54,0:06:23.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雨好像停了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:25.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊 天气真好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.81,0:06:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.65,0:06:33.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了对付海兽 而出动的美国战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:39.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,君子不近刑人 危险远离 危险远离
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.52,0:06:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那架飞机…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.43,0:06:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是『蔚蓝之水』
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:49.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再过三天我们会折返法国一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.83,0:06:51.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到时就让你们下船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:54.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢您 梅比鲁舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.30,0:06:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是我第一次登上战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:06:59.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我可以四处参观吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要紧 尽管去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.71,0:07:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.92,0:07:08.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由你负责照顾这些孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.88,0:07:09.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.82,0:07:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大姐头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你真的要跟战舰硬拼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一切都是为了要得到 『蔚蓝之水』
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.91,0:07:34.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,舰尾左舷有船只接近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:35.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.78,0:07:42.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是那些孩子说的铁制船
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,副舰长 去找孩子们过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.59,0:07:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,告诉他们客人到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.09,0:07:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到舰桥去是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 舰长找你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.43,0:07:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.97,0:07:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好棒的船喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.74,0:08:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,艾尔顿先生 这艘船的全长是多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.21,0:08:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这种事是军事机密
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.98,0:08:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.12,0:08:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以参观舰桥喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:21.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,战舰是用来杀人的船
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.39,0:08:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你看到这种东西 竟然高兴成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太不正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,会吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.67,0:08:37.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.44,0:08:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们的客人到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.45,0:08:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的耶 是葛兰迪丝小姐他们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.98,0:08:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然还追到海上来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.25,0:08:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吧 副舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给他们两三发炮弹打声招呼 顺便警告他们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.32,0:08:56.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也可当作演习
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是 主炮发射准备
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.96,0:09:02.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,主炮发射准备
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.83,0:09:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大姐头 我想再离远点会比较安全
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:11.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说那是什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:13.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是距离再拉开就追不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.64,0:09:16.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 性命要紧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.81,0:09:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.85,0:09:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是贪生怕死 岂能当得了坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.32,0:09:22.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一切都是为了『蔚蓝之水』
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.60,0:09:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什么东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.00,0:09:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最新型的旋转炮塔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:39.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以水压驱动大炮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.37,0:09:41.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了不起的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.24,0:09:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,突然开炮太过份了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.45,0:09:54.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对坏人不需要手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:10:00.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好过份的船 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:02.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,桑森 韩森 准备应战
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.12,0:10:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的葛兰坦竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,白旗 快举白旗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.61,0:10:58.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:11:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说那什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.25,0:11:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,性命要紧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.16,0:11:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一开始就该这么做了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.03,0:11:14.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,副舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.70,0:11:15.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:17.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用吊臂把他们吊起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:19.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一到法国就交给警方查办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.97,0:11:20.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.51,0:12:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢招待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.45,0:12:42.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已经吃完了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.88,0:12:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,速度真快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.85,0:12:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 因为肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且好好吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.12,0:12:50.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.23,0:12:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我会转告伙房的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:55.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怪了 这不是你做的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.86,0:12:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不不 怎么会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.57,0:12:59.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然看不太出来 但我可是位学者喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.70,0:13:01.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,学者？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.10,0:13:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是身负 美利坚合众国总统的秘密任务
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.07,0:13:09.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因此搭上这艘军舰的 海洋学家 艾尔顿博士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.31,0:13:12.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在这艘船上地位仅次于舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.91,0:13:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以你才没有穿军服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.92,0:13:17.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.59,0:13:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听好了 强
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.12,0:13:22.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所有的生物都能分为两种
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.66,0:13:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吃的 跟难吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.90,0:13:28.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,至于这条鱼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,属于好吃的那一类
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.84,0:13:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.41,0:13:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你几乎都没吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.31,0:13:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？不吃？ 如此美味的食物？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 那真是太不幸了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人的一生就是吃 睡 玩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就只有这三项
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.59,0:13:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而你竟然白白舍弃其中一项
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:14:01.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是…太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.76,0:14:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.00,0:14:07.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不想杀害动物 来成就自己的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.17,0:14:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来你是素食主义者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.27,0:14:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.57,0:14:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不晓得吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.14,0:14:16.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是指不吃肉和鱼的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗？娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.58,0:14:23.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是大王在吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王你吃没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.73,0:14:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对了 你们想不想知道 这艘船的秘密任务是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.20,0:14:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以说出来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.07,0:14:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要你们答应不说出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.27,0:14:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就只告诉你们两人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.37,0:14:46.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 我答应
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.14,0:14:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其实这艘战舰正在追捕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.48,0:14:51.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在世界各海域出没的大海兽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.65,0:14:53.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么嘛 那我早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.82,0:14:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早就知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.05,0:14:57.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在巴黎的报纸看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.32,0:15:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 这种事 为什么要当成机密？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海兽又不会看报纸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.00,0:15:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总之 那是军事机密
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:14.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 有这么大艘战舰的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.50,0:15:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无论怎样的海兽 都不是对手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:23.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里是主桅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.05,0:15:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,舰首右舷发现疑似海兽物体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.92,0:15:28.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,正朝方位104前进
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.75,0:15:32.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全员就战斗位置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.39,0:15:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,重复一次 全员就战斗位置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.23,0:15:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全员就战斗位置…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.10,0:15:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们也走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:57.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是那个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.92,0:16:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.82,0:16:04.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,启航才4天就碰上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:06.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们实在走运
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.99,0:16:08.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,开启所有炮门
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,目标为右舷大型生物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.96,0:16:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行 别开火
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.50,0:16:14.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.30,0:16:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算是海兽也是生物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:20.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么可以杀它 太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.84,0:16:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那可不成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.64,0:16:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那家伙不晓得害死多少船员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.58,0:16:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.75,0:16:31.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,测距完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.01,0:16:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所有主炮开始追踪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.75,0:16:36.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,方位瞄准仪至射击指挥仪 传导正常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,各炮连动追针开始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.55,0:16:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,目标距离1万2千 速度30节
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.76,0:16:45.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,30节？这怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.16,0:16:47.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难以相信它竟然比本舰还快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.20,0:16:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所有主炮完成发射准备
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:53.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,糟糕 被它给逃了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.94,0:16:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真奇怪 好像有东西在追它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.51,0:16:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它没事了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.14,0:17:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.31,0:17:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吵死了 给我出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都怪你多嘴说那些 我们才会被赶出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.46,0:17:23.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,本来就不该杀生嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.57,0:17:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太不可原谅了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.07,0:17:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对吧 大王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:32.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的 你满脑子就只有早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.04,0:17:34.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你明白大王在说什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.04,0:17:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 其他动物多少也懂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.08,0:17:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但我却不懂那只海兽的心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.98,0:17:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那家伙是只邪恶的海兽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.15,0:17:46.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎么可能会懂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:49.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海兽从古代就住在海中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.89,0:17:53.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是后来出现的人类 想要猎杀海兽的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.60,0:17:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗨 你们在吵什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.00,0:17:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海兽怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.60,0:17:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你没看到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.03,0:18:03.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我人在厨房 刚好错过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.61,0:18:05.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在厨房做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.74,0:18:09.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在做要给海兽的饵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,香肠是海兽的饵吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.58,0:18:15.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 这也是军事机密
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.42,0:18:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂它香肠？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.92,0:18:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它又不是大王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.52,0:18:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里无论什么都是军事机密
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.09,0:18:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为是军舰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.49,0:18:26.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这也是没办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.89,0:18:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们看 这样海兽就会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.54,0:18:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.47,0:18:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.98,0:18:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那边也有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.28,0:18:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,数万年前残存下来的海兽 可不会只有一头
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.28,0:18:51.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是没有一公一母当夫妻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.09,0:18:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就生不出小孩了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.92,0:18:55.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来它们是夫妻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.19,0:18:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真不愧是海洋学家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.10,0:19:07.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.60,0:19:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,潜进海里了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.87,0:19:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海兽是爬虫类
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.31,0:19:13.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了换气还会浮出海面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.74,0:19:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,从那边过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.65,0:19:22.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海兽从右舷后方接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.08,0:19:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,速度32节
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.92,0:19:25.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,主炮测距还没好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.69,0:19:27.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行 目标太过靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,副炮呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.82,0:19:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来不及
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.19,0:19:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.56,0:19:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行 要撞上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.11,0:19:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真走运！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.68,0:19:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第二管区进水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.11,0:19:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,注水至第三火药库 动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,复原倾斜 启动右舷排水帮浦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:19:59.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.12,0:20:01.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这艘军舰装甲全由钢铁打造
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.39,0:20:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是用钢铁做成的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.06,0:20:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然能在船底开洞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.39,0:20:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那家伙真的是生物吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.16,0:20:10.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海兽于左舷徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该死的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.40,0:20:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,右舷齐发
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.80,0:20:15.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定要宰了它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.85,0:20:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,弹开了？是金属的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.11,0:20:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,另一头海兽呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.82,0:20:29.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在正下方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.02,0:20:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它在追逐那只海兽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.86,0:20:41.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船会沉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.06,0:20:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.56,0:20:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这艘可是美国海军的 最新战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.07,0:20:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说的对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.20,0:20:53.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,集近代科学精华所建造出的 亚伯拉罕号是不会沉的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.17,0:20:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海兽死了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.95,0:21:01.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,击中了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.22,0:21:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它还活着 又潜下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.05,0:21:05.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错 快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.02,0:21:07.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不然会被杀死的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海兽朝舰首右舷笔直前进
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.87,0:21:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,左舵 左满舵！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.90,0:21:21.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,左满舵！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.24,0:21:22.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太惊人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.00,0:21:25.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遭主炮直接命中 竟然还能活命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.44,0:21:28.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,左舷前方有物体靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.94,0:21:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.05,0:21:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.05,0:21:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.15,0:21:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是鱼雷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.03,0:21:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.14,0:21:55.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.14,0:21:56.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.84,0:22:01.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行 舵转不过来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.94,0:22:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,左舷倾斜7度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.38,0:22:05.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,主炮转盘无法转动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.15,0:22:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第三 第五管区进水
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.91,0:22:08.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第一炮塔无法旋转
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.08,0:22:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.78,0:22:10.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,实在太不像话了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.12,0:22:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全力进行左舷排水
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.81,0:22:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.64,0:22:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.15,0:22:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.32,0:22:44.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.52,0:22:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.36,0:22:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.62,0:22:52.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 我找不到大王
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.89,0:22:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王不见了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.43,0:22:56.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 而且战舰也…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.60,0:23:02.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们没有注意到我们落海了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.87,0:23:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是艾尔顿…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.37,0:23:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行 你看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.84,0:23:08.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,舵被击中了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.38,0:23:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已经无法折返了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.44,0:23:11.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.31,0:23:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.75,0:23:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.59,0:23:22.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是我的飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.86,0:23:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.53,0:23:28.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,满脑子就只有大王
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.33,0:23:35.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 如果那真是鱼雷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.97,0:23:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那只海兽的真面目 究竟会是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.85,0:23:54.58,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.62,0:24:02.62,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该怎么应付心中的焦急才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.70,0:24:07.66,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就要看不清远方的梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.74,0:24:12.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我喃喃自语 仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.17,0:24:21.05,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与你的约定耀眼闪烁着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.12,0:24:31.15,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Try 安慰的话语 是传达不到内心的风
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.23,0:24:39.89,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然背负的不安逐渐膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.97,0:24:44.17,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但这是我自己的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.24,0:24:48.83,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一个人应该也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.91,0:24:58.15,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使跌倒或感到迷惘 仍然有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.96,0:25:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们两个人与一只动物
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.70,0:25:13.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被吸进神秘大海兽的嘴巴里
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.40,0:25:14.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海兽的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.70,0:25:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其实是世界上首艘实用潜水艇
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.97,0:25:20.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 这艘船一定是海盗船
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.64,0:25:21.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不会啦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.78,0:25:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,发明出这么棒东西的人 不可能会是坏人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.88,0:25:29.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海底两万里 下一回 『万能潜水艇鹦鹉螺号』
